{"tid":1778340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［告急］ 白領工會街站需要義工！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-12-11T01:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T11:02:30.000Z","uid":210612,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"aa33f9e6bdc9cd48997ab1f8ac21acc1703d842a","tid":1778340,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T01:03:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時間無多 招義工！！<br />\nJJ 插瀝青求救</span><br />\n<br />\n日期：12月13號 (五)<br />\n地點：尖東噴水池<br />\n時間：下午1時至3時<br />\n<br />\n日期：12月14號 (六)<br />\n地點：觀塘 駿業街遊樂場<br />\n            及 荔枝角 D2 出口<br />\n時間：中午12時至2時<br />\n<br />\n需要：您 你 妳 在座咁多位朋友<br />\n<br />\n而家就係我地白領工會需要你嘅時間喇<br />\n<br />\n💪💪💪義工招募💪💪💪<br />\n如果您都好想為工會為大家為自己出一分力<br />\n我地好希望您加入做義工一齊幫忙<br />\n誠邀您有興趣嘅<br />\n可以TG pm @whereisym <br />\n只要簡單比你tg名同埋你想參與邊一日義工就得㗎喇🤓<br />\n<br />\n🤝🤝🤝幫忙範圍🤝🤝🤝<br />\n1. 派poster<br />\n2. 比form人填<br />\n3. Show QR code<br />\n<br />\n📝當天我地將會📝<br />\n1. 收已填online form嘅會費<br />\n2. 招新會員，即場填表同收會費<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n👨&zwj;💻👩&zwj;💻👔👗👜👞👠✏🖊🗒📝💼📎<br />\n📌更多白領工會的最新消息📌<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://facebook.com/hkwccu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fhkwccu&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=d10b3e06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/hkwccu</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkwccu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkwccu&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=469f4f27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkwccu</a><br />\nTG Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkwccu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkwccu&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=129648ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkwccu</a><br />\nEmail: hkwccu@gmail.com"},{"pid":"79474ae853c6fa9de8a28d43834e36fd54d9959b","tid":1778340,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T01:05: